title: Nevosoft - Farm Craft FINAL - New Dash Game [h33t][Wendy99]
description:
Farm Craft FINAL

Create your very own garden in Farm Craft, 
a colorful challenge featuring bushels of farm fun! 
Ginger has always shown a special talent for nurturing plants 
and animals. When AgroCorporation, a powerful conglomerate, wants 
to develop the land outside of town, it&#039;s up to Ginger to use 
her knack for farming to save the village and its farms! 
Help Ginger plant and harvest a variety of produce, feed and 
look after the livestock, and save each family farm from the 
onslaught of industry. Design each farm according to 
your own taste and expand your operation with new tools, plants, 
and animals at each level. A charming trip to farm fun, 
join Ginger on her delightful adventure in Farm Craft today.


Thanx to TAC-CM
